snippet.title: Wildfire Swap Launch Trailer
snippet.description: Fight fires in Wildfire Swap! Create breaks between fires and homes by solving tile swapping puzzles. "...we hope that as [players] overcome the puzzles, they get some sense of the enormous amount of planning and hard work fire fighting teams put in to contain these fires." https://store.steampowered.com/app/1216030/Wildfire_Swap/ #indiegames #puzzlegames #steamgames
